00:55:43,520 --> 00:55:45,200
Za nimi.

718
00:56:04,950 --> 00:56:07,070
Jsi v pohodě?

719
00:56:07,070 --> 00:56:08,870
Ano.

720
00:56:09,870 --> 00:56:13,750
Po celou dobu... jsi žil...

